146
00:07:45,909 --> 00:07:46,470
Really?

147
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,000
Of course.

148
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,700
I told you

149
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:51,670
Yuan Shanqing

150
