166
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:37,669
What do you mean?

167
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,429
You two went to the hospital

168
00:08:39,429 --> 00:08:40,890
in the middle of the night.

169
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:44,230
Went to the hospital in the middle of the night?

170
00:08:44,230 --> 00:08:45,910
What's wrong with going to the hospital?

171
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:46,970
Is there a problem?

172
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,980
You two came out together

173
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,090
